# Examples

* enigmatic_client - Reference client.

## Building External Programs

The `Enigmatic_Client` API is exposed as the installable library
`libenigmatic_client` with pkg-config name `enigmatic_client`.

Compile an external client program with:

```
cc my_program.c $(pkg-config --cflags --libs enigmatic_client) -o my_program
```

Headers are installed under `enigmatic/`, for example:

```
#include "Enigmatic_Client.h"
```
